<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FAQ - LUME</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Aboreto&family=Jost&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f8f5f2;
      color: #2c1810;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .faq-container {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .faq-sidebar {
      min-width: 200px;
      max-width: 220px;
      background: none;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
    .faq-sidebar ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .faq-sidebar li {
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .faq-sidebar a {
      color: #3a2414;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .faq-sidebar a.active, .faq-sidebar a:hover {
      color: #8a9b7d;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .faq-main {
      flex: 1;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }
    .faq-title {
      font-family: 'Aboreto', cursive;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: #3a2414;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    }
    .faq-intro {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #2c1810;
    }
    .accordion-button {
      background: none;
      color: #2c1810;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0d8cc;
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 1.1rem 0.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
      color: #8a9b7d;
      background: #f5e6d3;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d4b996;
    }
    .accordion-item {
      border: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0d8cc;
      background: none;
    }
    .accordion-body {
      background: none;
      color: #2c1810;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 0.5rem 1.2rem 0.5rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .faq-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      .faq-sidebar {
        max-width: 100%;
        min-width: 0;
        padding-top: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .faq-main {
        padding-top: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/user/header") %>
  <div class="faq-container">
    <nav class="faq-sidebar">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/faqs" class="active">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="/shipping-returns">Shipping</a></li>
        <li><a href="/track-order">Track My Order</a></li>
        <li><a href="/returns">Returns</a></li>
        <li><a href="/recycle-upgrade">Recycle & Upgrade</a></li>
        <li><a href="/jewellery-care">Jewellery Care</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <main class="faq-main">
      <div class="faq-title">ASSISTANCE & CUSTOMER CARE</div>
      <div class="faq-intro">
        <b>Welcome to our FAQ section!</b> Here, you'll find answers to the most frequently asked questions, all in one easy-to-navigate section. If you have any further queries, please do not hesitate to reach out to our team directly.
      </div>
      <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
              What is Gold Vermeil?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Gold vermeil is a thick layer of gold (at least 2.5 microns) electroplated over sterling silver. It offers the look and feel of solid gold at a more affordable price.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
I’m buying a gift but don’t know the ring size!            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
Please refer to our ring size guide for help. If buying a ring as a gift, we recommend choosing a general size and ordering a ring sizer. If the ring doesn’t fit, we can exchange* it for the correct size (provided it is unworn and in perfect condition).

*Please note we cannot exchange solid gold items, but we can assist you with resizing if needed. Please reach out to our team for more information.            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
              How long do Made to Order pieces take to make?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Made to order pieces typically take 2-4 weeks to craft, depending on the complexity and availability of materials.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
              What is your return policy?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              We accept returns within 7 days of delivery for unworn, undamaged items in their original packaging. Please see our Return Policy for details.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
              Am I able to return or exchange a made-to-order piece?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Made-to-order and customized pieces are not eligible for return or exchange unless there is a manufacturing defect.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq6">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
              Customisable or bespoke?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq6" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Yes, we offer customisation and bespoke services. Please contact us to discuss your ideas and requirements.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq7">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7">
              I'm not sure if the size I ordered will fit perfectly. Can I swap sizes?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq7" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              We offer one free size exchange within 7 days of delivery, provided the item is unworn and in original condition.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
  <%- include("../partials/user/fooret.ejs") %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 